David Jeremiah Devotion mobile App will help you mature spiritually, as great revelation insight of God's word by David Jeremiah comes to you everyday. The sole purpose is to bring the word of God to more people through his servant.
David Jeremiah Devotion mobile App is a tool which provides an easy way to read your daily devotion on the go , it provides an easy to use interface which organizes the readings into calendar dates making it
easy for you to navigate through the readings for the day and weeks.
descriptionShort: David Jeremiah Devotion mobile App will help you mature spiritually
title: David Jeremiah Devotion
